# Intuition
This code uses airline ticket information to construct a valid itinerary starting from the departure airport "JFK" and organizing destinations into a dictionary-style graph. It manages the routes from departure to arrival using a stack, adding them to a new itinerary when there are no more destinations. The final itinerary is reversed to obtain the correct order.

---

