1, sort from/to pairs in lexical order, and store them in dict.
2, start the route with current city in the smallest lexical order, it may not cover all the cities, but it is still a valid route because eventually you will go through.
3, append the last city to the end, and loop 2 -> 3 till all cities are visited.

