This qus is basically the extension of the graph qus **where we have to find the path from the given  virteces  to the whole virteces in directed graph ... **

There we deal with the integer here we are dealing with the string .. 
One thing to check is the we have to use backtraking first delete that node from the list and then add after that in dfs .. **Why ?**
Bcz if we have adjList like  = "jfk" - {"atl","now"} , "atl" - {"jfk"} 
first we go the jfk as given in the qus and then will go the atl as lexically smaller and when we go the adjList of atl it will go the jfk and then again we call the atl .. So , this will create a cycle and will trap into it .. so to get out of that trap we have to remove the "atl" from the "jfk" adjList .. 

